         <t:abstract><t:ab>The Ethiopic version of Regula Pachomii is a partial translation from Greek. It consists of three parts:
         1) the so-called Rules of the Angel (from the "Lausiac History" by Palladius) 2) a text based upon the Greek Excerpta
       3) a late Ethiopian compilation attributed to Pachomius but unattested in other languages.</t:ab></t:abstract>
